Name: [Dodge] Magnetic Dart
Desc: When in the Counter state, Agent EX Special Attacks and Dodge Counter <color=#2BAD00>Interrupt level is increased</color>, and all Agents' DMG increases by <color=#2BAD00>50%</color>.
Desc2: A dart with a powerful magnet installed on the tip that allows you to hit the bullseye every time even with your eyes closed, as long as you don't throw it off the dart board.
